  if( i < 5 )

  else if(i > 90)

Todo 14) Function Loop

fun2 = function(arg5)
{
  sec13 = seq(from=1, to=arg5)
  vec13 = c()
  for (i in 1:arg5)
  {
    if( i < 5 )
    {vec13[i] = sec13[i] * 10}
    else if(i > 90)
    {vec13[i] = sec13[i] * 10}
    else 
    {vec13[i] = sec13[i] * 0.1}
  }
  print(vec13)
}
